author: kfogel
msg: * www/propaganda.html, www/project_links.html: Reorganize so that
each of these pages has appropriate material, and crosslink them.
Hosting sites are now listed in project_links.html, while
articles and reviews are listed in propaganda.html.  Also, move a
few individual entries to more appropriate categories, and fix
some formatting.
All this was motivated by the desire to link to Codestriker, which
I'll do in a separate commit.
